  "title": "Mass Hiring Technician - Up to 3.6k / 5 days / EAST",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Global MNC in the manufacturing industry</li><li>Seeking for Manufacturing Technician x20</li><li>5 days work shift, fixed shift (Company Transport provided)</li><li>Nearest MRT: Upper Changi / Tampines</li></ul><p><strong>The Talent</strong></p><ul><li>NITEC or Higher NITEC or Diploma in Electrical, Electronics, Mechanical, Mechatronic, Microelectronics or any Engineering related studies</li><li>Experience in Assembly, Build, Test, Preventive Maintenance, Troubleshooting</li></ul><p><strong>The Job</strong></p><ul><li>Working in the Cleanroom environment</li><li>Responsible for maintenance and troubleshooting of the Tools and Equipment</li><li>Handling testing and assembled equipment</li><li>In-charge of the set-up and calibration of the equipment/machine/tool</li><li>Interpret complex electro-mechanical diagrams, drawings, and basic schematics.</li><li>Conduct precise measurements within tight tolerances</li><li>others duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Next Step</strong></p><ul><li>Simply click on 'Apply here' to drop your resume or email to <a href=\"mailto:weixiang.saw@adecco.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>weixiang.saw@adecco.com</strong></a></li><li>All shortlisted candidates will be contact</li></ul><p><br />Saw Wei Xiang</p><p>Direct Line: 6697 7975</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R24123075</p>",
